## Factory Pattern â PadrĂŁo ObrigatĂłrio

Toda instanciaĂ§ĂŁo de service deve passar por uma factory. A factory Ă© responsĂĄvel por injetar a implementaĂ§ĂŁo Prisma correta:

```typescript
// shared/factories/make-authenticate-service.ts
import { PrismaUsersRepository } from '@/repositories/prisma/prisma-users-repository';
import { AuthenticateService } from '@/modules/auth/authenticate.service';

export function makeAuthenticateService() {
  const repository = new PrismaUsersRepository();
  return new AuthenticateService(repository);
}
```

O controller sempre chama a factory â nunca instancia o service diretamente.

